Third Street Chai offers an exceptional non-GMO chai concentrate prepared from the finest all natural ingredients. Third Street Chai microbrews all their liquid concentrates with whole spices, which are freshly milled just before brewing. For their commitment to exceptional taste, body and consistency, they personally brew every drop of chai that bears the name Third Street Chai.
